<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَقَوْلِهِ:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#947721">{رَبَّنَا وَسِعْتَ كُلَّ شَيْءٍ رَّحْمَةً وَعِلْمًا}</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#947721">{وَكَانَ بِالْمُؤْمِنِينَ رَحِيمًا}</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#947721">{كَتَبَ رَبُّكُمْ عَلَى نَفْسِهِ الرَّحْمَةَ}</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#947721">{وَهُوَ الْغَفُورُ الرَّحِيمُ}</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#947721">{فَاللَّهُ خَيْرٌ حَافِظًا وَهُوَ أَرْحَمُ الرَّاحِمِينَ}</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>